VULCAN CONSTRUCTION MATERIALS, LP, SOUTHERN AND GULF COAST DIVISION, Plaintiff-Appellee v. MCLEA DEVELOPERS, INC., doing business as Leach Construction Company, Inc., Defendant-Appellant. No. 07-60455

Summary Calendar.

United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 25, 2007. Michael F. Rafferty, Harris, Shelton, Dunlap, Cobb & Ryder, Memphis, TN, for Plaintiff-Appellee. Perrin Nelson Smith, Jr., Gholson, Hicks & Nichols, Columbus, MS, for Defendant-Appellant. Before WIENER, BENAVIDES, and PRADO, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM: *

AFFIRMED. See 47.6.

Pursuant to 5th Cir. R. 47.5, the court has determined that this opinion should not be published and is not precedent except under the limited circumstances set forth in 5th Cir. R. 47.5.4.
